{"tid":1807942,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"解散警隊不如叫「成立新警隊—效忠香港市民」","createTime":"2020-01-02T05:16:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T06:02:04.000Z","uid":14918,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f24a57f5cfac0dd1df0d9e2b6049f467aea4cd05","tid":1807942,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:16:47.000Z","msg":"之前有篇社論講過，外國係唔止得一隊執法機構 i.e.警隊 <br />\n好似英國法國，有警隊、憲兵<br />\n美國有 國會警察、法院警察，係完全獨立運行既部隊<br />\n<br />\n香港唔應該得一隊黑警壟斷執法權力<br />\n所以要成立新警隊&mdash;效忠香港市民/立法會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>相關Post</strong><br />\n解散警隊, 唔應該再鳩叫<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1807577\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1807577</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9b23baaa3ed270379e7010ac8e72fca84fbc5032","tid":1807942,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5adc2cf5742808f6dd37cab66af24dc110a0d57","tid":1807942,"uid":321859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:19:37.000Z","msg":"咁只係3萬黑警變6萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d858063978cfee9a6863be745838436745b73e5","tid":1807942,"uid":239205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5adc2cf5742808f6dd37cab66af24dc110a0d57","tid":1807942,"uid":321859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:19:37.000Z","msg":"咁只係3萬黑警變6萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:27:36.000Z","msg":"只要新既執法部門唔係屬於政府就冇事"},{"pid":"cfd723946458ff65dad58abb3339133ab6905a98","tid":1807942,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:28:57.000Z","msg":"100億請啲戰地保安公司嚟香港都夠喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e18a1a1894535e13b3f5a45e38da996ec72271","tid":1807942,"uid":73089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s